{"1":{"w":[{"b":"0.06","h":"0.1","c":"وَٱلضُّحَىٰ","d":"wal-ḍuḥā","e":"By the morning brightness","i":"وَالضُّحٰىۙ"}],"a":{"g":"By the morning brightness"}},"2":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.15","c":"وَٱلَّيۡلِ","d":"wa-al-layli","e":"And the night","i":"وَالَّيۡلِ"},{"b":"1.0","h":"1.53","c":"إِذَا","d":"idhā","e":"when","i":"اِذَا"},{"b":"1.6","h":"2.53","c":"سَجَىٰ","d":"sajā","e":"it covers with darkness","i":"سَجٰىۙ"}],"a":{"g":"And [by] the night when it covers with darkness,"}},"3":{"w":[{"b":"0.07","h":"0.06","c":"مَا","d":"mā","e":"Not","i":"مَا"},{"b":"0.5","h":"0.67","c":"وَدَّعَكَ","d":"waddaʿaka","e":"has forsaken you","i":"وَدَّعَكَ"},{"b":"1.5","h":"2.38","c":"رَبُّكَ","d":"rabbuka","e":"your Lord","i":"رَبُّكَ"},{"b":"2.4","h":"3.76","c":"وَمَا","d":"wamā","e":"and not","i":"وَمَا"},{"b":"3.0","h":"4.72","c":"قَلَىٰ","d":"qalā","e":"He is displeased","i":"قَلٰىؕ"}],"a":{"g":"Your Lord has not taken leave of you, [O Muhammad], nor has He detested [you]."}},"4":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.1","c":"وَلَلۡأٓخِرَةُ","d":"walalākhiratu","e":"And surely the Hereafter","i":"وَلَـلۡاٰخِرَةُ"},{"b":"1.7","h":"2.59","c":"خَيۡرٞ","d":"khayrun","e":"(is) better","i":"خَيۡرٌ"},{"b":"2.4","h":"3.74","c":"لَّكَ","d":"laka","e":"for you","i":"لَّكَ"},{"b":"3.0","h":"4.72","c":"مِنَ","d":"mina","e":"than","i":"مِنَ"},{"b":"3.4","h":"5.35","c":"ٱلۡأُولَىٰ","d":"l-ūlā","e":"the first","i":"الۡاُوۡلٰىؕ"}],"a":{"g":"And the Hereafter is better for you than the first [life]."}},"5":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.45","c":"وَلَسَوۡفَ","d":"walasawfa","e":"And soon","i":"وَلَسَوۡفَ"},{"b":"1.0","h":"1.96","c":"يُعۡطِيكَ","d":"yuʿ'ṭīka","e":"will give you","i":"يُعۡطِيۡكَ"},{"b":"2.2","h":"3.68","c":"رَبُّكَ","d":"rabbuka","e":"your Lord","i":"رَبُّكَ"},{"b":"3.1","h":"5.17","c":"فَتَرۡضَىٰٓ","d":"fatarḍā","e":"then you will be satisfied","i":"فَتَرۡضٰىؕ"}],"a":{"g":"And your Lord is going to give you, and you will be satisfied."}},"6":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.2","c":"أَلَمۡ","d":"alam","e":"Did not","i":"اَلَمۡ"},{"b":"0.6","h":"0.85","c":"يَجِدۡكَ","d":"yajid'ka","e":"He find you","i":"يَجِدۡكَ"},{"b":"1.4","h":"2.32","c":"يَتِيمٗا","d":"yatīman","e":"an orphan","i":"يَتِيۡمًا"},{"b":"3.3","h":"4.44","c":"فَـَٔاوَىٰ","d":"faāwā","e":"and gave shelter","i":"فَاٰوٰى"}],"a":{"g":"Did He not find you an orphan and give [you] refuge?"}},"7":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.25","c":"وَوَجَدَكَ","d":"wawajadaka","e":"And He found you","i":"وَوَجَدَكَ"},{"b":"1.0","h":"1.75","c":"ضَآلّٗا","d":"ḍāllan","e":"lost","i":"ضَآ"},{"b":"5.5","h":"6.51","c":"فَهَدَىٰ","d":"fahadā","e":"so He guided","i":"لًّا فَهَدٰى"}],"a":{"g":"And He found you lost and guided [you],"}},"8":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.2","c":"وَوَجَدَكَ","d":"wawajadaka","e":"And He found you","i":"وَوَجَدَكَ"},{"b":"1.0","h":"1.67","c":"عَآئِلٗا","d":"ʿāilan","e":"in need","i":"عَآٮِٕلًا"},{"b":"4.1","h":"4.75","c":"فَأَغۡنَىٰ","d":"fa-aghnā","e":"so He made self-sufficient","i":"فَاَغۡنٰىؕ"}],"a":{"g":"And He found you poor and made [you] self-sufficient."}},"9":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.6","c":"فَأَمَّا","d":"fa-ammā","e":"So as for","i":"فَاَمَّا"},{"b":"1.5","h":"1.95","c":"ٱلۡيَتِيمَ","d":"l-yatīma","e":"the orphan","i":"الۡيَتِيۡمَ"},{"b":"2.7","h":"3.74","c":"فَلَا","d":"falā","e":"then (do) not","i":"فَلَا"},{"b":"3.4","h":"4.8","c":"تَقۡهَرۡ","d":"taqhar","e":"oppress","i":"تَقۡهَرۡؕ"}],"a":{"g":"So as for the orphan, do not oppress [him]."}},"10":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.42","c":"وَأَمَّا","d":"wa-ammā","e":"And as for","i":"وَاَمَّا"},{"b":"1.2","h":"2.26","c":"ٱلسَّآئِلَ","d":"l-sāila","e":"him who asks","i":"السَّآٮِٕلَ"},{"b":"4.1","h":"5.04","c":"فَلَا","d":"falā","e":"then (do) not","i":"فَلَا"},{"b":"4.7","h":"6.22","c":"تَنۡهَرۡ","d":"tanhar","e":"repel","i":"تَنۡهَرۡؕ"}],"a":{"g":"And as for the petitioner, do not repel [him]."}},"11":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.06","c":"وَأَمَّا","d":"wa-ammā","e":"But as for","i":"وَاَمَّا"},{"b":"1.7","h":"2.09","c":"بِنِعۡمَةِ","d":"biniʿ'mati","e":"(the) Favor","i":"بِنِعۡمَةِ"},{"b":"2.8","h":"3.85","c":"رَبِّكَ","d":"rabbika","e":"(of) your Lord","i":"رَبِّكَ"},{"b":"3.7","h":"5.48","c":"فَحَدِّثۡ","d":"faḥaddith","e":"narrate","i":"فَحَدِّثۡ"}],"a":{"g":"But as for the favor of your Lord, report [it]."}}}